import{post,get,upload}from"src/request/api";import{stringify}from"querystring";// 查询限时任务列表
export var timingTasks=function timingTasks(data){return get('/api/v1/app/timing/query-timing-tasks',data);};// 查询限时任务详情
export var taskDetail=function taskDetail(data){return get('/api/v1/app/timing/task-detail',data);};// 查询我的限时任务详情
export var myTaskDetail=function myTaskDetail(data){return get('/api/v1/app/timing/my-task-detail',data);};// 拿到限时任务
export var obtainTimingTask=function obtainTimingTask(data){return get('/api/v1/app/timing/obtain-timing-task',data);};// 上传图片
